snippet.title: Infinity Nikki - Overview Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description: Watch the new trailer for Infinity Nikki, a glamourous dress-up adventure game, coming to PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, and the App Store. Sign ups for its closed beta are available now.
